snippet.title: Ancient Gods (by Linh Lam Quang) IOS Gameplay Video (HD)
snippet.description:
App description:

Ancient Gods is a new combination of gacha and deck-building rogue-lite. You will experience unique adventures, and build OP decks from hundreds of cards and characters to conquer new challenges.

App Store Link:https://apps.apple.com/nz/app/ancient-gods-card-battle-rpg/id6444331833
